<div class="title">Euphoric State of Consciousness</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Steven+Pollock&Exact=1">Steven Pollock</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Steven Pollock. "Euphoric State of Consciousness: An Experience with Amanita muscaria (exp1753)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 11, 2000. erowid.org/exp/1753</div>

